      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "You can use the Notification section to set basic settings for your push including: The title of the Push, the message, an in-app image, or if it is dismissible.",
      "pos": [
        3807,
        3968
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "Many notification settings are specific to the platform of your device.",
      "pos": [
        3969,
        4040
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "You can select whether your push will be sent \"in app\" or \"out of app\" or both.",
      "pos": [
        4041,
        4120
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "(Remember that users can \"opt-in\" or \"opt-out\" of \"out of app\" Pushes at the Operating System level on their devices, and Azure Mobile Engagement will not be able to override this setting.",
      "pos": [
        4121,
        4309
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "Also remember that the Reach API handles \"in app\" and \"out of app\" Pushes.",
      "pos": [
        4310,
        4384
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "The Push API can be used to handle \"out of app\" pushes too.) Pushes can be customized with pictures or HTML content, including deep links for linking outside of your App or to another location in your App (Android SDK 2.1.0 or later intent categories required).",
      "pos": [
        4385,
        4646
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "You can change the icon or iOS badge, and send either text or web content (a popup with html content, URL link to another location either inside or outside of the app).",
      "pos": [
        4647,
        4815
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "You can also make Android devices ring or vibrate with the Push.",
      "pos": [
        4816,
        4880
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "(Remember that you will need the correct SDK permissions in your Android manifest file to ring or vibrate a device.) There is currently no industry standard for Android \"Big Picture\" sizes, since screen sizes are different on every device, but 400x100 pictures work on almost any screen size.",
      "pos": [
        4881,
        5173
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "Delivery Types:",
      "pos": [
        5179,
